參考文獻[編輯]


^ Barker, Craig J. International Law and International Relations. Continuum International Publishing Group, 2000, ISBN 0-8264-5028-8, p. 2.
^ Zeitschrift für Assyriologie und vorderasiatische Archäologie. Walter de Gruyter & Co, 1999, p. 149.
^ The Peace Treaty Between Ramses II and Hattusili III
^ Fitzgerald, Stephanie. Ramses II: Egyptian Pharaoh, Warrior, and Builder, p. 64. Compass Point Books, 2008. ISBN 978-0-7565-3836-1










